<bold>Judaism&#x000a0;&#x000a0;</bold>
</p>
        <p>Judaism is the expression of the covenant that God established with the Children of Israel. Judaism includes texts, practices, theological positions, and forms of organization.</p>
        <p><italic toggle="yes">Beliefs</italic>&#x000a0;</p>
        <list list-type="bullet">
